  "an1.347:1.0": "",
  "an1.347:1.1": "in the same way, those who have gained the taste of the goal, the taste of the Dhamma, the taste of release are few, ",
  "an1.347:1.2": "while those who have not gained the taste of the goal, the taste of the Dhamma, the taste of release are more numerous. ",
  "an1.347:1.3": "“Therefore, monks, you should train yourselves: ",
  "an1.347:1.4": "‘We will gain the taste of the goal, the taste of the Dhamma, the taste of release.’ ",
  "an1.347:1.5": "That’s how you should train yourselves.”",
